## Troubleshooting Performed

Initially, the EC2 instance was not accessible.

The following components were verified:

* Public IP Assignment
* Internet Gateway Attachment
* Route Table Configuration
* Network ACL Rules
* Security Group Rules
* Apache Service Status
* HTTPS Configuration

After correcting the network configuration and enabling SSL, both HTTP and HTTPS connectivity were successfully established.

